---
import { Copy, Brain, Settings, Download } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works-5 section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Cara Kerja Clipcash AI</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Gak perlu skill editing, biar AI yang ngerjain semuanya buat lo.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <Copy class="h-8 w-8" />
        </div>
        <h3>Copy Link Video</h3>
        <p>Tinggal copy link YouTube video panjang yang mau lo jadiin klip pendek.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <Brain class="h-8 w-8" />
        </div>
        <h3>AI Proses Video</h3>
        <p>Sistem otomatis potong momen viral, deteksi hook, dan kasih subtitle keren.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <Settings class="h-8 w-8" />
        </div>
        <h3>Konfigurasi</h3>
        <p>Atur posisi subtitle, warna, atau edit sedikit sesuai selera lo.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <Download class="h-8 w-8" />
        </div>
        <h3>Download & Cuan</h3>
        <p>Klip siap upload ke TikTok/Reels. Fokus monetisasi dan tunggu hasilnya.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works-5 {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: #0A0A0A;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .step-card {
    background: #151515;
    padding: 40px 30px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    position: relative;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-yellow, #FAB005);
    transform: translateY(-10px);
  }

  .step-num {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    right: 20px;
    font-size: 64px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: rgba(250, 176, 5, 0.1);
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: rgba(250, 176, 5, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-yellow, #FAB005);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .step-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .step-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
